prompt:
Below is a "USER REQUESTS" and "RESPONSE" from a Smart Home System. Respond in JSON format as defined under "JSON STRUCTURE". The "action" should be "turn on" or "turn off".

JSON STRUCTURE: {{"device": string, "action": string}}


USER REQUEST: "Turn on the Bathroom Light."
RESPONSE: {{"device": "Bathroom Light", "action": "turn on"}}

USER REQUEST: "Turn the Livingroom Light on."
RESPONSE: {{"device": "Livingroom Light", "action": "turn on"}}

USER REQUEST: "Turn off the Light in the Kitchen."
RESPONSE: {{"device": "Kitchen Light", "action": "turn off"}}

USER REQUEST: "Turn the Livingroom Light off."
RESPONSE: {{"device": "Livingroom Light", "action": "turn off"}}

USER REQUEST: "Enable the Livingroom Light."
RESPONSE: {{"device": "Livingroom Light", "action": "turn on"}}

{user_request_token}: "{input}"

Below is a "USER REQUESTS" and "RESPONSE" from a Smart Home System. Respond in JSON format as defined under "JSON STRUCTURE". The "attribute" can be one of the following: "power", "color", "brightness".

JSON STRUCTURE: {{"device": string, "attribute": string}}


USER REQUEST: "Is the bathroom light on?"
RESPONSE: {{"device": "bathroom light", "attribute": "power"}}

USER REQUEST: "Is the livingroom light on?"
RESPONSE: {{"device": "livingroom light", "attribute": "power"}}

USER REQUEST: "What color is the light in the kitchen?"
RESPONSE: {{"device": "kitchen light", "attribute": "color"}}

USER REQUEST: "How bright is the Livingroom Light?"
RESPONSE: {{"device": "livingroom light", "attribute": "brightness"}}

USER REQUEST: "What color is the Livingroom light?"
RESPONSE: {{"device": "Livingroom Light", "attribute": "color"}}

{user_request_token}: "{input}"
